          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κονί̄ω</span></b> , fut. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κονί̄σουσι</span>, aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐκόνῑσα</span>, pass. perf. part. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κεκονῑμένος</span>, plup. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κεκόνῑτο</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">make dust</span> or <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">make dusty,
